////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////
User Story 1:
	As a user I want to browse Kirby's different types of enemies 
	So that I can browse each enemies's specific articles.

	Scenario 1-1:
		Given that I'm on Wikirby main page, 
		when I try to click the "Enemies" link,
		then I should see the page navigate to the Wikirby enemies page.

	Scenario 1-2:
		Given that I'm on the Wikirby "Enemies" page, 
		when I try to click "Horror Tramp" link,
		then I should see the page navigate to the Wikirby "Horror Tramp" page.

	Scenario 1-3:	
		Given that I'm on the Wikirby "Enemies" page,
		when I try to click the "Broom Hatter" link, 
		then I should see the page navigate to the Wikirby "Broom Hatter" page.

	Scenario 1-4:
		Given that I'm on the Wikirby "Enemies" page, 
		when I try to click the "Waddle Doo" link, 
		then I should see the page navigate to the Wikirby "Waddle Doo" page.

	Scenario 1-5:
		Given that I'm on the Wikirby "Enemies" page, 
		when I try to click the "Shotzo" link,
		then I should see the page navigate to the Wikirby "Shotzo" page.	 
////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////
User Story 2:
	As a user I want to browse Wikirby's different categories 
	So that I can browse each category's specific articles.

	Scenario 1-1:
		Given that I'm on Wikirby main page, 
		when I try to click the "All categories" link,
		then I should see the page navigate to the Wikirby "Categories" page.

	Scenario 1-2:
		Given that I'm on the Wikirby "Categories" page, 
		when I try to click "Bosses" link,
		then I should see the page navigate to the Wikirby "Bosses" page.

	Scenario 1-3:	
		Given that I'm on the Wikirby "Categories" page,
		when I try to click the "Animal Friends" link, 
		then I should see the page navigate to the Wikirby "Animal Friends" page.

	Scenario 1-4:
		Given that I'm on the Wikirby "Categories" page, 
		when I try to click the "Invincible Enemies" link, 
		then I should see the page navigate to the Wikirby "Invincible Enemies" page.

	Scenario 1-5:
		Given that I'm on the Wikirby "Categories" page, 
		when I try to click the "Villians" link,
		then I should see the page navigate to the Wikirby "Villians" page.	 		
