User Story 3:
	As a user I want to be able to go to other Wiki websites  
	So that I can look at different Wikis and explore.

	Scenario 1-1:
		Given that I'm on Wikirby main page, 
		when I try to click the "Bulbapedia" link,
		then I should see the page navigate to the Bublapedia main page.

	Scenario 1-2:
		Given that I'm on the Wikirby main page, 
		when I try to click "Metroid Wiki" link,
		then I should see the page navigate to the Metroid Wiki main page.

	Scenario 1-3:	
		Given that I'm on the Wikirby main page,
		when I try to click the "Pikmin Fanon" link, 
		then I should see the page navigate to the Pikmin Fanon main page.

	Scenario 1-4:
		Given that I'm on the Wikirby main page, 
		when I try to click the "Super Mario Wiki" link, 
		then I should see the page navigate to the Super Mario Wiki main page.

	Scenario 1-5:
		Given that I'm on the Wikirby main page, 
		when I try to click the "Zelda Wiki" link,
		then I should see the page navigate to the Zelda Wiki main page.	 	
