User Story 4:
	As a user I want to browse the Characters page 
	So that I can look at the different characters in Kirby's universe.

	Scenario 1-1:
		Given that I'm on Wikirby main page, 
		when I try to click the "Characters" link,
		then I should see the page navigate to the Wikirby "Characters" page.

	Scenario 1-2:
		Given that I'm on the Wikirby "Characters" page, 
		when I try to click "Adeleine" link,
		then I should see the page navigate to the Wikirby "Adeleine" page.

	Scenario 1-3:	
		Given that I'm on the Wikirby "Characters" page,
		when I try to click the "Gooey" link, 
		then I should see the page navigate to the Wikirby "Gooey" page.

	Scenario 1-4:
		Given that I'm on the Wikirby "Characters" page, 
		when I try to click the "Meta Knight" link, 
		then I should see the page navigate to the Wikirby "Meta Knight" page.

	Scenario 1-5:
		Given that I'm on the Wikirby "Characters" page, 
		when I try to click the "Zero" link,
		then I should see the page navigate to the Wikirby "Zero" page.	 
